summary: Racemenu Preset for my character I made for Enderal. Half Arazalean.
descriptionHtml:
Roryk (Rawr-Rick) is Arazalean by base build and half Aeterna. Though the Aeterna are no longer purely what they once were, I'd thought I would make something subtle to distinguish features between human and elf mixed breeds in my perspective.

Mods used:
